@startuml seq-oauth-login
title OAuth Login (Google / Apple)

actor Parent as P
participant "Next.js PWA" as PWA
participant "Fastify API\nAuthController" as API
participant "AuthService" as Auth
participant "Keycloak" as KC
participant "Google / Apple" as OAuth
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

P -> PWA : Tap "Sign in with Google"
PWA -> API : GET /auth/oauth/google
API --> PWA : 302 Redirect to\nKeycloak auth endpoint
PWA --> P : Redirect to Google
P -> OAuth : Authenticate & consent
OAuth --> PWA : Redirect with auth code
PWA -> API : GET /auth/oauth/callback\n?code=...&state=...
API -> API : Validate state parameter
API -> Auth : federateOAuthUser(GOOGLE, code)
Auth -> KC : Exchange code for tokens\nvia Keycloak broker
KC -> OAuth : Token exchange
OAuth --> KC : id_token, access_token
KC --> Auth : Keycloak tokens + user info
Auth -> DB : UPSERT Account\n(link or create)
Auth --> API : account + tokens
API --> PWA : 200 { accessToken,\nset refreshToken cookie }
PWA --> P : Logged in

@enduml
